Summary of changes:
- Removed extraneous publication metadata footnote:
  - deleted `[^1]` marker from body and its footnote definition at the end.
- Preserved equation content and kept equation numbering consistent:
  - retained `$$\tag{1} ... $$` and verified all in-text `(1)` references resolve to that display equation.
- Improved markdown paragraph structure/readability:
  - added missing blank-line paragraph breaks in clear boundary cases (notably in the dialogue turns and one missed prose break).
  - added one missing paragraph break after the `***` divider.
- Minor markdown cleanup:
  - fixed one awkward wrapped phrase (`"classify Bayesians"` on one line).
  - normalized the References section into a proper markdown list for cleaner rendering.

Self-check completed:
- Intended paragraph breaks are blank-line separated.
- No unresolved in-text equation-number references remain.
